Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育園今天有義賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是...五百祗...先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副模樣除了我還能是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是本大爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直用手按著不放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土...鳩...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在大街上睡午覺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果困了 還是回家進被窩好好睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才 才 才不是在睡午覺!

Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:14.17,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:14.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:14.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:21.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:21.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:34.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:34.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:41.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:41.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:52.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:52.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:15.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:15.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

