Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...謎之生命體.2號.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 這到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見我這個樣子還不明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生不知怎麼滿身是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都看不出來嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 聽我說!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天陰沉沉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿肯定能賣出去的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有肯定能賣出去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在保育園裝布偶也差不多膩味了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去熊那裡大吃一頓年輪蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是開在這種奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(熊記年輪蛋糕店)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(正在營業中)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一個長蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我4個熱香餅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一個香草的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了 熱香餅三人份 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍候 正在烤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱香餅六個裝做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長蛋糕怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 還要2分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是生意興隆啊 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是瑞祥的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了功夫就是不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再增加些品種吧 巧克力什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不壞嘛 就那麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真成蛋糕師了啊 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初還以為會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼的就順其自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連挖苦都不起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 對了 宅配服務也開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是熊記年輪蛋糕店嗎 等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?不是平時一直來的那位鳥先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...這樣啊 是兼職的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經也有過拚命兼職的時期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恣意妄為的僱主使喚來使喚去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話就這麼多嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去過像迷宮之館一樣的那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一個不可思議的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間多得讓人迷路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(休息中)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你們現在這副悠然自得的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快把你們以前是什麼樣的都忘了啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體也不壞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛太厚是有點不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過注意點的話也沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都覺得我從出生起一直是這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然發生過那種事 簡直就像夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說是噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經過去很久了呢 從那以來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜地想一想 我們根本沒有勝算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手太厲害了 根本是在被動挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潰敗得也真是快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候好像踩到誰了 是誰來的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?!是玄琥大人嗎 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是過去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且當時也沒空為了那些小事發火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的我們啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 什麼也別說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不認同 規矩就是規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能一邊烤年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊等時間來解決問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是反省的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了這種可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不能想也不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再跟天界開打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可就不是熊啊小鳥的就算完得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓我變成泰迪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他就不用變鳥了 變成鳥食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那可不要的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有自己變成可愛的角色太狡猾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總之 麻煩是無論如何絕對不要惹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 別吃啊 那是我重要的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果手信也只肯給一盒 小氣鬼熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 吃了甜的再來點鹹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 吃了鹹的再吃這個年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有鹹的東西呢?沒有呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過醬油味也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在這心情還是鹽味合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是能有種衝擊感的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我解圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 球又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它那麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要命 臭小鬼都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就踢個球有什麼好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是你們的食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 這是本大爺的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還配不上吃年輪蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就此收手的話就把你們變成烤全...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~咧~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可太吃力了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快把火以外的東西吐出來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子好重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪上加霜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那東西的話就可以一口氣弄乾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾燥機裡比想像中要艱苦得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...什麼地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那裡的蔬菜店...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 肚子餓了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要留到回去之後慢慢享受的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是忍不住要先吃的小鬼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聞上去很香的氣味是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那迷之生命體是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到mocono land
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宵的ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要高興地忘乎所以然後迷路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請盡情玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來闖進了奇怪的地方了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那香味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!哪個看起來都很好吃的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說了我是布偶又不是布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點逃出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被別人把年輪蛋糕的盒子拿走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要哪個都沒問題的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打靶啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要那個藍色的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?我看看...我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 沒打中 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈個屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭了 這回...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線衝我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這回一定能中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?感覺它是不是動了下?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會動嘛 是爸爸不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是打不中 爸爸越是燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一定會弄到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 下一發會怎麼樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 身為一個成年人不要那麼認真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給老朽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看老朽這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前可是被稱為靶神加奈的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪冒出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦 不倒下的話是不算的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼大家齊心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合個屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只藍色的還沒倒下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要變成小孩子的玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了啊 找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 剛剛是掉下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 大家也都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 倒霉透頂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡的話就稍微能放心...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是發生了這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為海報被人撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一直跑到這個時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有人來義賣會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那個規模也太小了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算海報不被人撕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個保育園的拍賣會也不該抱太大期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會變成這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是當時不說要辦義賣會才對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是決定了要做就要好好做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遇到困難也不可以放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是被水弄濕 被狙擊手狙擊也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 最重要的就是要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為沒有客人就那麼失望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 賣掉了這麼多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴娃娃也賣出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了小鳩 我也淘到了好東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在那發呆發到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的客人 人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小鳩的努力 才有這麼多客人來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒那種事..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:19:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了小鳩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝你特意過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也買了不少有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過其實很希望從小鳩手裡買到東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有賣自己的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣的怎麼樣了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個也沒賣出去...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不知是雞是企鵝還是羊的謎之生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有人想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我買一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是很有個性的設計呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂 堂元先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是美好的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是過的很悲慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你有沒有聽本大爺說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是這樣嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 嘛 保住了那件重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果來說還是好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以後馬上開吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要好好品嚐那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是哪個呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了 本大爺的年輪蛋糕沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 回去保育園拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 年輪蛋糕的話早賣掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生說了要拿能賣的東西回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個能賣的東西就是指年輪蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是謝謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的分數...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對義賣會的熱情八十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上讓我失望的扣分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合計分數是負三百分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失望是我的錯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是道歉就能解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把我做的可愛小兔子送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 作為贈品多送給你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.65,0:22:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加上這邊可愛的小熊和小羊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來這個哪個是哪個根本就分不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一堆都是迷之生命體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?太過分了五百祗先生

Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...寒風的溫暖.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議
